des:
Dragons Lunch is a skill to entertain preschoolers. 

It is a short rhyme that makes children giggle and want it played again.

You can say:

"Alexa, open Dragons Lunch"
"Alexa, start Dragons Lunch"
"Alexa, play Dragons Lunch"
